{"tid":2314166,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星級髮型師Jacky Ma不敵胃癌逝世","createTime":"2020-12-06T10:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T11:22:59.000Z","uid":48360,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6d1ab914c1aaf3c519897c29646b555700b17da9","tid":2314166,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:48:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=415580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415580&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2jw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=84311c38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415580&h=5345efa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=415580</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-12-06-17-10-58cjukyy8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-12-06-17-10-58cjukyy8X.jpg&h=3aaa53d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年患上胃癌的星級髮型師Jacky Ma（馬桂燦），經過兩年治療終不敵病魔逝世，終年59歲。<br />\n<br />\nJacky Ma擔任首席總監的Headquarters Hair Salon Hong Kong下午在facebook專頁公布他的死訊，指Jacky Ma上周四（12月3日）下午在瑪麗醫院安詳離世，家人陪伴在側，稍後公布喪禮詳情。<br />\n<br />\nJacky Ma（馬桂燦）2018年患胃癌，曾在瑪麗醫院進行切胃手術保命，帖文提到他上月中做了最後一場hair show，又提到他的金句「剪得唔好唔放手，剪得唔靚唔畀走。」<br />\n<br />\n娛圈多名紅星，包括李克勤、軟硬天師、草蜢、達明一派、鄭伊健等都是Jacky Ma的顧客，關係友好。2004年，Jacky Ma與李麗珍傳出戀情，太太李靜婷當年爆料，指丈夫和李麗珍有不倫之戀，雙方子女也目睹兩人不尋常關係，事件成為城中熱話，Jacky Ma沒有否認，更揚言李麗珍是他的最愛，願意離婚，放棄事業再迎娶李麗珍，不過李麗珍表示與Jacky Ma從沒有發生性關係。<br />\n<br />\nJacky Ma與李靜婷育有一子一女，李靜婷於2010年因中風離世。"},{"pid":"4cab2e693220105661a86700d8cf7698a748d6ac","tid":2314166,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"Jacky Ma死訊全文：<br />\n我們謹此以沉痛的心情通知大家，Headquarters Salon 創始人及首席總監Jacky Ma經過兩年多的抗病路後，於12月3日下午在瑪麗醫院安詳離世，家人均陪伴在側。<br />\nJacky 於11月中演繹人生中最後一場Hair show後光榮引退，回歸天父的懷抱，我們都以他為榮！<br />\n<br />\n他的slogan:<br />\n[剪得唔好唔放手，剪得唔靚唔俾走]，我們日後都會以他的精神繼續前行！<br />\n在此謹代表其家人感謝所有曾經給予Jacky幫忙及支持的醫護人員。<br />\n喪禮詳情將於稍後公報，唯希望各界能於此段時間給予家人空間處理各項事宜。<br />\n<br />\nPhoto / Headquarters Hair Salon Hong Kong FB page"},{"pid":"d1583fcd6b05c4d503dabcb45d3fb310c2cfc588","tid":2314166,"uid":132106,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06d2af7d77257059c4bcf172f85fad7cfe22e5d","tid":2314166,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"當年同李麗珍單野都幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1ecd15ddfe71c4f1fde33c6f73decdb843eca9","tid":2314166,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"剪髮師"},{"pid":"0ceccaa40681c8178b1fe147634198c701b35744","tid":2314166,"uid":48360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c06d2af7d77257059c4bcf172f85fad7cfe22e5d","tid":2314166,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"當年同李麗珍單野都幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"係, 仲有佢老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26ff31fe589acd5d0b1e095808ef0b6c1650902","tid":2314166,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"髮型師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb14f05d878bb3754d31da92c0dc25643dab6de3","tid":2314166,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c06d2af7d77257059c4bcf172f85fad7cfe22e5d","tid":2314166,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"當年同李麗珍單野都幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so